- measuring - compass, ruler angle
- categorised items e.g the main addItems menu has categories - bluefor, opfor, mv which when clicked on takes the user to a sub menu   
    - i.e click on bluefor, then opens a menu with, infantry, mortars, engineers etc
- export map



